This is the source code of Plurkism,
a growl application for pushing plurk messages

to Build:

	1. use XCode 3 or 4 to open this project
	2. build Plurkism and PlurkismPane
	
to Run:

	1. Copy PlurkismPane.prefPane to ~/Library/PreferencePanes/
	2. Copy Plurkism.app to /Applications
	3. Run Plurkism.app, fill in account and password in popuped preference Pane


